Meet the #HottestCollegeInAmerica during the QS Top MBA World Tour fair on Tuesday, November 24th at the Sofitel Saigon Plaza in Ho Chi Minh City! Janaki Vijay, Associate Director of Graduate Recruitment for the University of Cincinnati Lindner College of Business will be on hand to help you learn about our nationally-recognized business school, ranked among the top 40 public MBA programs in the United States. We offer campus and online MBA options, as well as eight specialized master's degrees.

15:30: Registration opens
17:15-17:35: Presentation from University of Cincinnati
18:30-21:00: Explore the MBA fair

